data.description: ***RARE assumable LOAN with 2.75% interest rate*** or seller will pay $10k concessions towards buying down interest rate. Spacious house at a great price don't let this one pass you by. Come see this 5 BDRM 4 BTH home, Garden Heights in Mansfield ISD! Perfect location with easy access to 360 and 287. Within walking distance to the neighborhood pool. You'll see soaring ceilings, a neutral palette, stunning curved staircase & 2 living areas down. This home is great for entertaining with its open concept living room, floor to ceiling stone fireplace, formal dining & kitchen complete with butler's pantry, granite, island, breakfast bar, ss appliances, gas stove, ample cabinets for storage & prep. Downstairs Primary bedroom with on-suite bathroom featuring, large tub, dual sinks, separate shower & walk in closet. Home office & full bath downstairs as well.  Game & media rooms upstairs makes for the perfect kids retreat!
